{"tid":459090,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[轉]史杜列治痛罵FIFA：我邊有咁慢！","createTime":"2017-11-05T13:18:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T14:24:43.000Z","uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7d13879a0eb1687b25999d2e127bc5132e119942","tid":459090,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=Hvgrx4ZACs2XLgKAvaCYyi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=70e91a2f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】不要誤會，史杜列治抱怨的不是國際足協，而是電玩足球遊戲《FIFA》，因為在遊戲中他的個人數據太不合理了。<br />\n<br />\n日前英格蘭國家隊發表了一段短片，主角是隊中前線拍檔史杜列治（Daniel Sturridge）及史達寧（Raheem Sterling），看看他們互相了解的程度有多深。他們在影片中各自透露了不少秘密，如史杜列治最愛看的電視節目是甚麼，又或者是史達寧有畏高等等。但談到2人在著名足球遊戲FIFA當中的數據時，才是片中高潮。<br />\n<br />\n看來2人都不常玩遊戲，因為這款遊戲其實一早已經發行，各球員的數據亦已被談論了不少時候。只是當工作人員告訴史杜列治他在遊戲中的速度數據只有76時，他與史達寧都只能瞠目結舌。史杜列治更以開玩笑的語氣「責備」遊戲的製作人員：「我是英超最快的球員之一，這個數字對我的自尊，對我的名號來說是不尊重吧？這是誰決定的？快點辭退他們吧！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BIiSwxLz2Ok\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBIiSwxLz2Ok&d=Hvgrx4ZACs2XLgKAvaCYyi7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=5bf03a6c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BIiSwxLz2Ok</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/3/543/19444145543/19451430533_600x346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F3%2F543%2F19444145543%2F19451430533_600x346.jpg&h=a5965f9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nEA FIFA 真係亂評分 無90速 最少都有87~89掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/05/211803_e62dc27d3be63432c2602316eda929be.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F05%2F211803_e62dc27d3be63432c2602316eda929be.jpg&h=4fa6d7bd&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"ca5bb1ed79633c9a0ce4b57036c40872f28792db","tid":459090,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T13:21:12.000Z","msg":"史達寧最少98啦"},{"pid":"bedb86ea6e3c72bdd5455931c9bacd45bc43009c","tid":459090,"uid":5006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:22:59.000Z","msg":"Pes合理好多 佢起pes入面真係幾快"},{"pid":"c4810050cb17efc268581abb1c3a3e9487fd7d2d","tid":459090,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T14:24:43.000Z","msg":"未傷之前就係"}]}